flowchart TD
    S([Insert(H,stu)]) --> A[SearchById查重]
    A --> B{学号已存在?}
    B -->|是重复| E1[输出:学号XX已存在 return ERROR]
    B -->|否| C[addr=HashFunc p=new HashNode]
    C --> D{p==NULL?}
    D -->|是| E2[return OVERFLOW]
    D -->|否| F[p->data=stu 头插:H[addr]=p]
    F --> G[输出:成功添加 return OK]
    style S fill:#C8E6C9,stroke:#2E7D32,stroke-width:2px
    style G fill:#C8E6C9,stroke:#2E7D32,stroke-width:2px
    style B fill:#FFF8E1,stroke:#F57F17
    style D fill:#FFF8E1,stroke:#F57F17
    style E1 fill:#FFEBEE,stroke:#C62828
    style E2 fill:#FFEBEE,stroke:#C62828